client.proxy

Class ClientCommunicator

  • java.lang.Object
    • client.proxy.ClientCommunicator

  • public class ClientCommunicator
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    isaachartung The ClientCommunicator receives java objects, serializes them, and sends them to the server. It is also responsible for receiving serialized objects from the server, deserializing them, and returning the new java object to its caller.
